<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Außer Betrieb</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        .notice-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 85%;
            border-top: 6px solid #e74c3c;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #666;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="notice-card">
        <div class="icon">🛑</div>
        <h1>Außer Betrieb</h1>
        <p>Der Wartungsprotokoll Generator wurde außer Betrieb genommen.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
